{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"If I can leave you with one big idea today,"},{"time":3000,"text":"it's that the whole of the data"},{"time":5000,"text":"in which we consume"},{"time":7000,"text":"is greater that the sum of the parts,"},{"time":9000,"text":"and instead of thinking about information overload,"},{"time":12000,"text":"what I'd like you to think about is how"},{"time":14000,"text":"we can use information so that patterns pop"},{"time":17000,"text":"and we can see trends that would otherwise be invisible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":20000,"text":"So what we're looking at right here is a typical mortality chart"},{"time":23000,"text":"organized by age."},{"time":25000,"text":"This tool that I'm using here is a little experiment."},{"time":27000,"text":"It's called Pivot, and with Pivot what I can do"},{"time":30000,"text":"is I can choose to filter in one particular cause of deaths -- say, accidents."},{"time":34000,"text":"And, right away, I see there's a different pattern that emerges."},{"time":37000,"text":"This is because, in the mid-area here,"},{"time":39000,"text":"people are at their most active,"},{"time":41000,"text":"and over here they're at their most frail."},{"time":43000,"text":"We can step back out again"},{"time":45000,"text":"and then reorganize the data by cause of death,"},{"time":47000,"text":"seeing that circulatory diseases and cancer"},{"time":50000,"text":"are the usual suspects, but not for everyone."},{"time":53000,"text":"If we go ahead and we filter by age --"},{"time":56000,"text":"say 40 years or less --"},{"time":58000,"text":"we see that accidents are actually"},{"time":60000,"text":"the greatest cause that people have to be worried about."},{"time":63000,"text":"And if you drill into that, it's especially the case for men."}]},{"cues":[{"time":66000,"text":"So you get the idea"},{"time":68000,"text":"that viewing information, viewing data in this way,"},{"time":71000,"text":"is a lot like swimming"},{"time":73000,"text":"in a living information info-graphic."},{"time":76000,"text":"And if we can do this for raw data,"},{"time":78000,"text":"why not do it for content as well?"},{"time":81000,"text":"So what we have right here"},{"time":83000,"text":"is the cover of every single Sports Illustrated"},{"time":86000,"text":"ever produced."},{"time":88000,"text":"It's all here; it's all on the web."},{"time":90000,"text":"You can go back to your rooms and try this after my talk."},{"time":93000,"text":"With Pivot, you can drill into a decade."},{"time":96000,"text":"You can drill into a particular year."},{"time":98000,"text":"You can jump right into a specific issue."},{"time":101000,"text":"So I'm looking at this; I see the athletes"},{"time":103000,"text":"that have appeared in this issue, the sports."},{"time":105000,"text":"I'm a Lance Armstrong fan, so I'll go ahead and I'll click on that,"},{"time":108000,"text":"which reveals, for me, all the issues"},{"time":110000,"text":"in which Lance Armstrong's been a part of."}]},{"cues":[{"time":112000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":115000,"text":"Now, if I want to just kind of take a peek at these,"},{"time":118000,"text":"I might think,"},{"time":120000,"text":"\"Well, what about taking a look at all of cycling?\""},{"time":122000,"text":"So I can step back, and expand on that."},{"time":124000,"text":"And I see Greg LeMond now."},{"time":126000,"text":"And so you get the idea that when you"},{"time":128000,"text":"navigate over information this way --"},{"time":130000,"text":"going narrower, broader,"},{"time":132000,"text":"backing in, backing out --"},{"time":134000,"text":"you're not searching, you're not browsing."},{"time":136000,"text":"You're doing something that's actually a little bit different."},{"time":138000,"text":"It's in between, and we think it changes"},{"time":141000,"text":"the way information can be used."}]},{"cues":[{"time":143000,"text":"So I want to extrapolate on this idea a bit"},{"time":145000,"text":"with something that's a little bit crazy."},{"time":147000,"text":"What we're done here is we've taken every single Wikipedia page"},{"time":150000,"text":"and we reduced it down to a little summary."},{"time":153000,"text":"So the summary consists of just a little synopsis"},{"time":156000,"text":"and an icon to indicate the topical area that it comes from."},{"time":159000,"text":"I'm only showing the top 500"},{"time":162000,"text":"most popular Wikipedia pages right here."},{"time":164000,"text":"But even in this limited view,"},{"time":166000,"text":"we can do a lot of things."},{"time":168000,"text":"Right away, we get a sense of what are the topical domains"},{"time":170000,"text":"that are most popular on Wikipedia."},{"time":172000,"text":"I'm going to go ahead and select government."},{"time":174000,"text":"Now, having selected government,"},{"time":177000,"text":"I can now see that the Wikipedia categories"},{"time":179000,"text":"that most frequently correspond to that"},{"time":181000,"text":"are Time magazine People of the Year."},{"time":184000,"text":"So this is really important because this is an insight"},{"time":187000,"text":"that was not contained within any one Wikipedia page."},{"time":190000,"text":"It's only possible to see that insight"},{"time":192000,"text":"when you step back and look at all of them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":195000,"text":"Looking at one of these particular summaries,"},{"time":197000,"text":"I can then drill into the concept of"},{"time":200000,"text":"Time magazine Person of the Year,"},{"time":202000,"text":"bringing up all of them."},{"time":204000,"text":"So looking at these people,"},{"time":206000,"text":"I can see that the majority come from government;"},{"time":210000,"text":"some have come from natural sciences;"},{"time":214000,"text":"some, fewer still, have come from business --"},{"time":218000,"text":"there's my boss --"},{"time":220000,"text":"and one has come from music."},{"time":225000,"text":"And interestingly enough,"},{"time":227000,"text":"Bono is also a TED Prize winner."},{"time":230000,"text":"So we can go, jump, and take a look at all the TED Prize winners."},{"time":233000,"text":"So you see, we're navigating the web for the first time"},{"time":236000,"text":"as if it's actually a web, not from page-to-page,"},{"time":239000,"text":"but at a higher level of abstraction."}]},{"cues":[{"time":241000,"text":"And so I want to show you one other thing"},{"time":243000,"text":"that may catch you a little bit by surprise."},{"time":246000,"text":"I'm just showing the New York Times website here."},{"time":249000,"text":"So Pivot, this application --"},{"time":251000,"text":"I don't want to call it a browser; it's really not a browser,"},{"time":253000,"text":"but you can view web pages with it --"},{"time":256000,"text":"and we bring that zoomable technology"},{"time":258000,"text":"to every single web page like this."},{"time":261000,"text":"So I can step back,"},{"time":264000,"text":"pop right back into a specific section."},{"time":266000,"text":"Now the reason why this is important is because,"},{"time":268000,"text":"by virtue of just viewing web pages in this way,"},{"time":271000,"text":"I can look at my entire browsing history"},{"time":273000,"text":"in the exact same way."},{"time":275000,"text":"So I can drill into what I've done"},{"time":277000,"text":"over specific time frames."},{"time":279000,"text":"Here, in fact, is the state"},{"time":281000,"text":"of all the demo that I just gave."},{"time":283000,"text":"And I can sort of replay some stuff that I was looking at earlier today."},{"time":286000,"text":"And, if I want to step back and look at everything,"},{"time":289000,"text":"I can slice and dice my history,"},{"time":291000,"text":"perhaps by my search history --"},{"time":293000,"text":"here, I was doing some nepotistic searching,"},{"time":295000,"text":"looking for Bing, over here for Live Labs Pivot."},{"time":298000,"text":"And from these, I can drill into the web page"},{"time":300000,"text":"and just launch them again."},{"time":302000,"text":"It's one metaphor repurposed multiple times,"},{"time":305000,"text":"and in each case it makes the whole greater"},{"time":307000,"text":"than the sum of the parts with the data."}]},{"cues":[{"time":309000,"text":"So right now, in this world,"},{"time":312000,"text":"we think about data as being this curse."},{"time":315000,"text":"We talk about the curse of information overload."},{"time":318000,"text":"We talk about drowning in data."},{"time":321000,"text":"What if we can actually turn that upside down"},{"time":323000,"text":"and turn the web upside down,"},{"time":325000,"text":"so that instead of navigating from one thing to the next,"},{"time":328000,"text":"we get used to the habit of being able to go from many things to many things,"},{"time":331000,"text":"and then being able to see the patterns"},{"time":333000,"text":"that were otherwise hidden?"},{"time":335000,"text":"If we can do that, then instead of being trapped in data,"},{"time":340000,"text":"we might actually extract information."},{"time":343000,"text":"And, instead of dealing just with information,"},{"time":345000,"text":"we can tease out knowledge."},{"time":347000,"text":"And if we get the knowledge, then maybe even there's wisdom to be found."}]},{"cues":[{"time":350000,"text":"So with that, I thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":352000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}